Well, I guess my name is random other person! I not only watched until the very end but enjoyed the unveiling or unpacking of your bags with great anticipation and joy. My goodness, we are so alike except I’m at least one generation older than you so you have some pretty sweet gadgets or helpful items that will make your travels so much easier than I’m m6 day. For instance I have 6 grand-babies whom all adore their remote controller yet I don’t remember them being in our life when my kids traveled so no great aid from remote. The other thing I truly fell in love with is your packing cubes. That would be so convenient for me! I don’t travel much anymore, when I do it’s either a 1-3 day trip for medical procedures or to travel and stay with family and help with my grands! I’m convinced that is THE WAY TO GO! I have never owned so many adorable swim suits but then never had your body either! Finn’s swimwear and shoes are almost as cute as he is... I can hardly wait to see him in them. I didn’t remember seeing sunglasses or little hat for him but you can always get there.
I just know you will all have the best of time. Great outfits and amount packed. Now waiting to see all the fun!
